 gravity if it can cascade effectively from\nthe large scale. We call this type of cloud t-type clouds. The analytical\nformula can be used to determine if gravity is dominating cloud evolution when\nthe column density probability distribution function (PDF) can be reliably\ndetermined.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2016 16:46:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Jul 2016 13:06:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-07"}
