c parts of the 2D shadow possess\nthe Wada property. Finally, we consider the possibility of following null\ngeodesics through event horizons, and chaos in the maximally-extended\nspacetime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2016 21:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2016 14:19:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2016 15:17:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-09"}
