tainties in turbulence or in the stellar\nmass profile. For highly inclined disks, this is a much more stringent\nrequirement than the usual sphere-of-influence criterion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2016 01:48:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-01"}
